metadata.name: Temple of Masks V2 "Look at my third eye"
metadata.description:
"Look at my third eye"  
Cryptofangs Genesis with Manifold contract.

Temple of Masks is a collaborative project created for Burning Man.  A project developed by metal sculptor Jason Gronlund with the support of Burning Man Arts.   Exclusive videoart pieces by Cryptofangs.

Credits:  
Video and Postproduction - Cryptofangs  
Artistic Direction - Cryptofangs / Jason Gronlund  
Mask Maker and Sculptor - Jason Gronlund  
Starring - Hanna-Katarina / Guyphytsy Aldalai  
Special Thanks - Burning Man Arts
